@startuml
title 票据签发

participant "web" as web #LightBlue
database "供票服务" as db1 #Lavender
filesystem "文件系统" as fs #Plum
entity "贸易背景" as tb2 #Thistle
queue "工作流" as wf3 #Orchid
actor "短信服务" as sms4 #MediumPurple


' Step-by-step interactions from Web to Supply Service for data entry steps
note over web : 
    <b>Step Details:</b>\n\n<b>User Actions</b>: \n- Click on Bill Issuance.\n- Fill in Drawer Information.\n- Enter Acceptor's Info.\n- Input Payee Data.\n- Optional Guarantor details if needed.\n- Complete bill information fields.\n- Proceed by clicking 'Next'.\n
    
end note 

== Initial Steps ==
db1 -> db1: Request Save First Set of Data (#8)
activate db1
alt Parameter Validation Successful(#9) then Create Trade Record(trade table,status=initial)(#10)\nCreate trade detail record(pre-generate IDs,bill_code)(#11)\nAdd asset records(asset status initialized at zero)(assert_table,#12)\nLink Asset ID via extension tables(issue_ext_tables). Then return generated codes back(web receives them after processing completes successfully.)else Invalid Parameters Detected During Checks End Process Early Without Saving Any Changes Made So Far Return Error Message Back To User Interface For Correction And Retry Attempt Later On If Needed Again After Fixing Issues Found Earlier Before Continuing Further Ahead With Next Stage Of Workflow Sequence Diagram Shown Here Below...endif deactivate db1



